OL,3,C'TV doctor' prescribed drugs for his
OL,4,Cfriends so he could use them
OL,6,FA GP from Lancashire who prescribed
OL,7,Fmore than 1,000 sleeping tablets to
OL,8,Ffriends - then took them back for his
OL,9,Fown use - has been suspended from the
OL,10,Fmedical register for nine months.
OL,12,FDr Andrew Foster's actions were
OL,13,Fbrought to light when a fellow GP at
OL,14,FBay Medical Group reported him to the
OL,15,FGeneral Medical Council (GMC) in June
OL,16,F2022 after becoming aware of his
OL,17,Factions.
OL,19,FDr Foster, 42, also referred himself
OL,20,Fto the GMC on the same day.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
