OL,3,C'TV doctor' prescribed drugs for his
OL,4,Cfriends so he could use them
OL,6,FAfter a lengthy Medical Practitioners'
OL,7,FTribunal Service (MPTS) hearing, which
OL,8,Fconcluded last month, Dr Foster was
OL,9,Fsuspended from the medical register
OL,10,Ffor nine months, with a 28-day appeal
OL,11,Fperiod. He can apply to return to
OL,12,Fpractise towards the end of his
OL,13,Fsuspension period.
OL,15,FThe MPTS has now published the full
OL,16,Fruling which goes into detail about Dr
OL,17,FFoster's offences. It describes how,
OL,18,Fbetween 2019 and 2022, he prescribed a
OL,19,Ftotal of 1,071 zopiclone sleeping
OL,20,Ftablets.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
