OL,3,C'TV doctor' prescribed drugs for his
OL,4,Cfriends so he could use them
OL,6,FThese include 23 prescriptions of 14
OL,7,Fx7.5mg zopiclone, one prescription of
OL,8,F7 x 7.5mg zopiclone and 27
OL,9,Fprescriptions of 28 x 7.35mg
OL,10,Fzopiclone. Dr Foster admitted
OL,11,Fprescribing the sleeping tablets
OL,12,Fwithout ever adequately assessing the
OL,13,Fpatient.
OL,15,FBetween 2019 and 2022 Dr Foster issued
OL,16,Fa total of 37 prescriptions for the
OL,17,Fpatient, which also included scripts
OL,18,Ffor diazepam and finasteride which can
OL,19,Fbe used to treat hair loss.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
