OL,3,C'TV doctor' prescribed drugs for his
OL,4,Cfriends so he could use them
OL,6,FTwo other patients each received a
OL,7,Ftotal of 27 prescriptions from Dr
OL,8,FFoster for drugs including diazepam
OL,9,Fand zopiclone which were in fact
OL,10,Fintended for his own use. Dr Foster
OL,11,Fwould arrange for the patients to
OL,12,Fcollect the medications and hand them
OL,13,Fback to him.
OL,15,FThe MPTS panel also heard that Dr
OL,16,FFoster had handed over a bottle of
OL,17,Fliquid morphine to a close family
OL,18,Fmember who had recently undergone an
OL,19,Foperation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
