OL,3,C'TV doctor' prescribed drugs for his
OL,4,Cfriends so he could use them
OL,6,FDr Foster told the panel he had
OL,7,F"bumped into the local pharmacist in
OL,8,Fthe car park when he had finished
OL,9,Fwork", who had then given him the
OL,10,Foramorph.
OL,12,FDr Foster's case was subsequently
OL,13,Freferred to police by NHS England
OL,14,FNorthwest in September 2023.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
