OL,3,C'TV doctor' prescribed drugs for his
OL,4,Cfriends so he could use them
OL,6,FFollowing an investigation by
OL,7,FLancashire Police, Dr Foster accepted
OL,8,Fa caution at Lancaster Police Station,
OL,9,Fadmitting that he unlawfully possessed
OL,10,Fa controlled Class B drug for a period
OL,11,Fof more than three years, between
OL,12,FMarch 2019 and November 2022.
OL,14,FAt the outset of the MPTS hearing
OL,15,FCatherine Rabaiotti, representing Dr
OL,16,FFoster, requested the proceedings be
OL,17,Fheard in private.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
