OL,6,FThe application was granted and some
OL,7,Fof the allegations found proven
OL,8,Fagainst Dr Foster, including the
OL,9,Fspecific drug he prescribed, remain
OL,10,Fredacted.
OL,12,FA number of testimonials were
OL,13,Fsubmitted in support of Dr Foster. One
OL,14,Fnurse wrote: "Dr Foster's remarkable
OL,15,Fjourney of self-reflection, growth and
OL,16,Fredemption serves as a shining example
OL,17,Fof the very best the medical
OL,18,Fprofession has to offer.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
