OL,6,F"His unwavering commitment to
OL,7,Fexcellence in his field makes him an
OL,8,Finvaluable asset to his patients, the
OL,9,Fcommunity and the medical profession
OL,10,Fas a whole. He is deeply respected and
OL,11,Fcherished by his colleagues, peers and
OL,12,Fpatients, and the surgery and the
OL,13,Fcommunity are enriched by his
OL,14,Fpresence."
