OL,3,C'TV doctor' prescribed drugs for his
OL,4,Cfriends so he could use them
OL,6,FDr Foster, who has previously been
OL,7,Finterviewed as an expert by BBC North
OL,8,FWest Tonight, told the MPTS panel that
OL,9,Fhe "struggled to say 'no' to people
OL,10,Fand that he was a people pleaser" but
OL,11,Fhas since reflected and learned from
OL,12,Fhis actions.
OL,14,FHe wrote in a statement: "I have spent
OL,15,Fa lot of time over the last couple of
OL,16,Fyears learning humility. Shedding the
OL,17,Ffacade of success and showing my flaws
OL,18,Fand faults and sharing them with
OL,19,Fpeople.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
