OL,3,C'TV doctor' prescribed drugs for his
OL,4,Cfriends so he could use them
OL,6,F"Being open and honest with my wife,
OL,7,Fmy family, friends and colleagues. It
OL,8,Fis liberating in a way that I have not
OL,9,Ffelt before. I am determined and
OL,10,Fcertain that this will never happen
OL,11,Fagain in the future."
OL,13,FDr Foster's offences were committed
OL,14,Fwhile he worked at Bay Medical Group.
OL,15,FFor the last two years he has worked
OL,16,Fat Bentham Medical Practice, which
OL,17,Fdeclined to comment on the MPTS ruling.
